---
source: crates/runtime/tests/models/search.rs
description: "SELECT id, answer, trunc(score, 3) as score FROM text_search(qs, 'secondary') where subject!='math' order by score desc LIMIT 4"
---
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                               |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Sort: score DESC NULLS FIRST, fetch=4                                                                                                                              |
|               |   Projection: text_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).id, text_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).answer, trunc(text_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).score, Int64(3)) AS score |
|               |     TableScan: text_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")) projection=[answer, id, score], full_filters=[text_search(qs, Utf8("secondary")).subject != Utf8("math")]        |
| physical_plan | SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@2 DESC], fetch=4                                                                                                                   |
|               |   SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@2 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                       |
|               |     ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@2 as answer, trunc(score@1, 3) as score]                                                                              |
|               |       FilterExec: subject@3 != math, projection=[id@0, score@1, answer@2]                                                                                          |
|               |         HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(id@0, id@1)], projection=[id@0, score@1, answer@2, subject@4]      |
|               |           CoalescePartitionsExec                                                                                                                                   |
|               |             CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                        |
|               |               RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                 |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                   CooperativeExec                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                     FullTextSearchTableExec q=secondary                                                                                                            |
|               |           RepartitionExec: partitioning=RoundRobinBatch(3), input_partitions=1                                                                                     |
|               |             FilterExec: subject@2 != math                                                                                                                          |
|               |               SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                   |
|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                 |
|               |                   DataSourceExec: partitions=1, partition_sizes=[2]                                                                                                |
|               |                                                                                                                                                                    |
+---------------+--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
